casebody.data:
Koury, d.b.a. Lauderette Services, Appellee, v. North Canton Properties, Appellant.

[Cite as Koury v. N. Canton Properties (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 1210.]

(No. 92-1628 Submitted September 28, 1993 Decided November 10, 1993.) Ralph S. Ladd, for appellee. Paul M. Greenberger, for appellant.

This cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
